## Summary
Amplitude's Mailchimp event streaming integration allows forwarding of Amplitude events and users to Mailchimp, requiring email mapping configuration, with options to filter events and select additional properties to send as Mailchimp event properties or merge fields, noting that transformed properties aren't supported and anonymous user events can't be streamed.

